# Implementation Plan - أدعية من القرآن (Quranic Supplications)

Add a new section dedicated to **أدعية من القرآن الكريم (Supplications from the Holy Quran)** featuring authentic Quranic supplications with Surah & Ayah citations, search filtering, and interactive actions (copy, share, bookmark, repeat counter).

---

## 📌 Proposed Placement

1. **Home Screen (`HomeScreen.kt`)**:
   - Add an **"أدعية من القرآن"** widget in the *Tools & Features* section with a emerald Quranic icon for 1-tap direct access.

2. **Azkar Section (`AzkarListScreen.kt`)**:
   - Feature **"أدعية من القرآن الكريم"** at the top of the Azkar categories list.

3. **Dedicated List Screen (`QuranicDuasScreen.kt`)**:
   - Accessible via route `Routes.QURANIC_DUAS`.
   - Displays a clean list of Quranic supplications with search, Surah & Ayah reference tags, and interactive action buttons (Copy, Share, Bookmark, Counter).

---

## 🛠️ User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> The supplications will be stored in `app/src/main/assets/quranic_duas.json` containing 44 authentic supplications from the Holy Quran with exact Surah and Ayah reference tags.

